          <title>Johni Broome's season-high 31 points and 14 rebounds lead No. 1 Auburn past Georgia 82-70</title>
          <description><![CDATA[AUBURN, Ala. (AP) — Johni Broome scored a season-high 31 points and added 14 rebounds as No. 1 Auburn defeated Georgia 82-70 on Saturday. For the second straight game, Auburn (25-2, 13-1 SEC) found itself in a tight contest against an unranked opponent before pulling away in the final minutes.]]></description>
